data.name: Evil Eye Awakening
data.desc: Special Summon 1 "Evil Eye" monster from your hand or GY, or, if "Evil Eye of Selene" is in your Spell & Trap Zone, you can Special Summon 1 "Evil Eye" monster from your Deck instead. You can only activate 1 "Evil Eye Awakening" per turn.

card_sets.set_name: 2020 Tin of Lost Memories Mega Pack
